# Frontend Patterns

## Navigation
- Use `navigateTo(pageId)` to switch sections
- Sections use `class="page-section" data-page="xxx"`
- Sidebar built dynamically via `SIDEBAR_MENUS` object

## API Calls
- Always use `authHeaders()` which includes JWT Bearer + X-Correlation-Id
- Use `apiUrl(path)` to resolve API_BASE correctly
- Handle errors: check `res.ok`, show `alert(await res.text())` for failures

## DOM Manipulation
- NEVER use `element.innerHTML +=` — it destroys event listeners
- Use `document.createElement()` + `appendChild()` for dynamic elements
- Use specific CSS selectors: `.page-section[data-page="xxx"]`

## Styling (NDD-inspired)
- Data grids use `.studio-grid` class with `.studio-grid__th` headers
- Cards use `.card.studio-card` with `.studio-header` toolbar pattern
- Forms use `.log-filter-group` with `<label>` + `<input>`
- Buttons: `.studio-btn--primary`, `.studio-btn--success`, `.studio-btn--outline`, `.studio-btn--accent`
